title: Pinnacle Bank Championship
text:
The Pinnacle Bank Championship is a <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="Korn%20Ferry%20Tour">Korn Ferry Tour</a>. It was first played in July 2017 at The Club at Indian Creek in <a href="Omaha%2C%20Nebraska">Omaha, Nebraska</a>.
Winners.
Bolded golfers graduated to the PGA Tour via the Korn Ferry Tour regular-season money list.
